headline: The Aspen Group Enhances Patient Experience with Planmeca Digital Imaging at Aspen Dental Locations Nationwide
summary: The Aspen Group (TAG), one of the largest and fastest-growing retail healthcare business support organizations in the U.S., today announced a new partnership with Planmeca to bring advanced digital imaging technology to Aspen Dental locations nationwide.
